    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras/0474f8540b9691a5fec1df7556e58710.avif?t=1749447567\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras_big/0474f8540b9691a5fec1df7556e58710.avif?t=1749447567 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dream Runner is a heartwarming, 2D adventure platformer following Soma's story of self-reflection as he's forced to master newfound abilities in order to save his lost best friend.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras/f5bc04f358adbc5c63feec86dc29b6ff.webp?t=1749447567\" width=275 height=21 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-crafted pixel art world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth &quot;flow-state&quot; precision platforming focused on combo-ing abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey of self-reflection as you venture deeper into the Dreamscape to rescue a lost friend</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles, catch butterflies, and venture through hidden paths as you move through Story Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your platforming abilities to the test in a flurry of post-game challenge levels in Arcade Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras/02c5223722b262e3c4d509d837555113.poster.avif?t=1749447567\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras/02c5223722b262e3c4d509d837555113.webm?t=1749447567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035870/extras/6a1bd5229d411fcfe20184e506d3d404.avif?t=1749447567\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p></li></ul>",
